  "short_description": "Friends or Frenemies? Team up or sabotage your friend in this fast-paced, 2-player brawler where you're literally tethered together. Set in a sci-fi world, play as a cute, unique animal wielding sports-inspired weapons. Beat up waves of killer robots, dodge attacks and score points to win!",
