  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TETHER BRAWL is an action-packed, top-down, 2-player game where co-operation is optional.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE THE ROBOT ONSLAUGHT </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play various game modes, where players tackle relentless robot waves. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From varied arenas to character uniqueness and different enemies, every match is exciting.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand united against the mechanical onslaught, or risk a crushing defeat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/1fe4b7cd3f370de20cc698ae6036ee36.poster.avif?t=1756142085\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/1fe4b7cd3f370de20cc698ae6036ee36.webm?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/1fe4b7cd3f370de20cc698ae6036ee36.mp4?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTER YOUR MOVES </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every character, from Jeremiah's bat-swinging might to Beccia's sharp throwing, demands skill. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly timing your skills and mastering abilities is essential.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead the charge and dominate the arena with calculated moves.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/793705896cf801791bc17fd1005a2978.poster.avif?t=1756142085\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/793705896cf801791bc17fd1005a2978.webm?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/793705896cf801791bc17fd1005a2978.mp4?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRUST IS OPTIONAL </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CO-OP mode emphasizes teamwork and synergy.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The competitive VERSUS mode offers both strategy and betrayal.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense PARTY matches are a balancing act of trust and competition.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/327f09fb1d08a9a11534ea3cd2e15fb3.poster.avif?t=1756142085\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/327f09fb1d08a9a11534ea3cd2e15fb3.webm?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/327f09fb1d08a9a11534ea3cd2e15fb3.mp4?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY WITH FRIENDS ONLINE USING STEAM'S REMOTE PLAY TOGETHER</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/4ca871d827caa6dc58b38d7aea838aa3.avif?t=1756142085\" width=598 height=142 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST AND GET READY FOR YOUR MATCH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/b4a6ff071b9c681784fc0b5ae3266852.poster.avif?t=1756142085\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/b4a6ff071b9c681784fc0b5ae3266852.webm?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/b4a6ff071b9c681784fc0b5ae3266852.mp4?t=1756142085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
